{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "赵无忌与上官刃（实为赵简易容）在狮山相会。上官刃以剑割开后颈皮肤露出赵简真面目，表明当年白玉老虎计划实为赵简为独霸权力谋害上官刃后冒充其身份潜入唐家堡。赵简坦承自己才是坏人，并透露已被唐傲利用上官怜怜的参汤下毒，功力消失四成。父子决定将计就计：赵简假装死于决斗中。赵无忌坚持与唐傲公平决斗，赵简以死明志，用内力震碎内脏嫁祸唐傲，逼迫无忌立誓报仇。赵无忌埋葬父亲后，唐傲现身，自曝日记为伪造，欲激怒赵无忌。赵无忌将计就计假装中计，约定在狮山决斗。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我知道你心里不肯相信，但又怕万一，对不对？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我看这样好了，明天我们再在这里见面，我保证到时一定会带来让你可以相信的证据。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "这点你信任我吧？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "不要！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不必太难过，我这样做，并不完全是要你相信我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "爹这样做，一半是为了赎罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我希望你有个心理准备。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你以为，是你上官大叔谋害了我，对不对？如今我的身份已经肯定了，你一定也知道，被杀的人，是上官大叔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "其实，白玉老虎的计划，完全是我设计的，自从我和你上官大叔经过李天回的易容之后，我的性情就开始转变。我时常想，假如有一天，大风堂能消灭了唐家堡，整个江湖都在我们掌管之下的时候，我、你上官大叔、以及司空，还是三个人分权管理吗？我忽然有一种冲动，我想，应该由我一个人独霸江湖才对。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "有这样的想法，我时常会变得烦躁无比，尤其一看到你上官大叔，我就会想，这个人要分享我的权力，我必须除去他。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "你没有想到司空大叔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你司空大叔是个没有野心的人，所以我一点也不忧虑。但是上官可不一样，他跟我一样，权力欲很大，我唯一比他强的，是比他深谋远虑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "有一天，我终于想出了白玉老虎的计划，既可一举消灭上官刃，也可以趁机混进唐家堡，伺机消灭唐家堡。于是，就在你大喜那一天，我把上官叫进密室，他做梦也想不到我会突下毒手，后面的事，你是知道的，我也不必多讲。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你爹才是个坏人，你知道吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不必太难过，我决定以毁容的方式来向你表明身份，就是想赎罪，我不应该谋害上官刃的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "爹已经没有用了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "唐傲那小子，已经在我身上下了毒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "怎么会？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "唐傲厉害，我相信他是利用怜怜炖参汤的机会，在参汤里下了毒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "那你..",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我刚才运气，血气不太通顺，功力大概消失了四成，唐傲这家伙！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "他为什么要这样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "他想利用你来除去我，同时，还可以利用这机会来打击你，你想想看，白玉雕龙的计划完全是假的，你杀我之后，他马上对你说出真相，这打击有多大？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "现在，我们必须将计就计。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "将计就计？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是的，你就假装把我杀了，让唐傲把真相告诉你，你要装成方寸大乱的样子，马上攻击他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我是他的对手吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "很难说，不过，他既然要用这个方法来对付你，这表示他对你也没有必胜的把握，不然，他根本什么花招都不出，对不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "所以，你一定要装成愤怒和后悔的样子，让他轻敌，而且，在过招的时候，一开始你就要弄出攻不成招，漏洞百出的打法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "万一他一下就抓我的漏洞，我岂不是自找死路？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不会的，以唐傲的个性，和对付你的方法，他一定会喜欢玩猫捉耗子的游戏，非逗得你求生不得求死不能的时候，才出手了断。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "这会不会太冒险？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不冒险，焉能有收获？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "可惜我做了一件错事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "什么错事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我怕你找我有什么大事，所以出来的时候，走得很秘密，唐家的人一点也不知道我去了哪里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "这件事错了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "现在想想是错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为以唐傲的个性，他一定会盯牢我，假如他知道我来了这里，一定会到这里，等着你我决斗以后，大大的嘲弄你一番。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹倒不用担心，我可做了一件对的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我曾经问过客栈里的伙计，怎么来这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "好，唐傲找不出我去了哪里的线索，一定会到客栈打听你的去处，他也一定会从伙计那里问出你来了这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "问题是我没说来，我只是问怎么走而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "够了，唐傲绝不会放过任何一丝线索的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "那他一定会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "也许他已经在附近找寻我们的下落了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "那我们现在怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们立刻把这里布置一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "布置？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是呀！弄得好像是经过一场激烈打斗的样子，让唐傲以为我们已经决斗过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "那爹你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我？这还不简单？我如今面目全非，装起死来，就格外像真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "你要装死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "这样唐傲才不会看出你是在装的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "可是..",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "怎么啦？你觉得我装死不吉利？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "那你..",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我跟唐傲有决斗之约。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "管他的，趁这个机会杀了他是最好的啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你跟他讲信用？他会是守信之人吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我是守信之人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "好吧，你守信好了，不过我可以告诉你，他等一会如果看到你，一定向你挑衅，逼你出手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "那样的话，就不是我先不守信了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "儿子呀，江湖险诈，你为什么一定要那么讲信用？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "在江湖上，不是以信用为优先吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "呸！我在江湖上打滚了这么多年，从来没有看过一个守信的人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "但是爹不是一直教我守信吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "教归教，面对事情的时候，就需要随机应变，知道吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你怎么这么拗？假如你爹像你这样，大风堂早就不知道到了哪里去了，还能在江湖上占一席之地吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "可是我..",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不要说了。你想想看，消灭了唐家堡之后，大风堂称霸江湖了，这个事业是属于谁的？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "当然是爹你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我？我能吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我的真面目已经揭穿了，大风堂的人都会知道我对上官刃下的毒手，我还够资格领导他们吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "那..",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "子承父业，整个大风堂都是你的了，你知道吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "是呀，我自毁容貌，除了向上官刃赎罪以外，另一个目的，也是想向大家表明，大风堂我不接管了，要全部交到你手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "所以，你要把大风堂管好的话，你必须了解，事情处理好最重要，信用，是要看对什么人才讲的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "这不合我的个性。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "个性？要讲个性，你最好隐居山林，在江湖上，只讲手段与目的，不讲个性的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹，你变了，变了很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "在江湖上浮沉了这么久，谁能不变？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "江湖真的这么险恶吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "比你想象的，还要险恶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "为了大风堂，为了继承历尽千辛万苦打下来的基业，你必须认清江湖上一切险恶的伎俩，面对它，才能屹立不移。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你一定要答应我，趁这个机会杀死唐傲。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹，你为什么一定要我做违背良心的事？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "良心？死人会有良心吗？死人还会讲良心吗？你不杀唐傲，唐傲就会杀你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我宁愿选择公平的决斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "公平的决斗？哼！唐傲用这个方法来对付你，他的心机，你还不清楚？这样还会公平吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹，你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "好阴险的唐傲呀！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你一定要替我报仇。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "报仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你现在知道唐傲有多狠毒了吧？",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "他下的慢性毒药，是不能见血的，一见血，我就变成这样。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "你现在怎么样了？爹！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我现在肝肠寸断，身体里面到处都在流血。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "怎么会这样？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "这就是唐傲狠毒的地方。他明知我跟你决斗，就算侥幸赢了，也难免会挂彩，他下的毒，一碰到血，我就，我就..",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "我送你去找大夫！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "没用了，我知道，我是回生乏术了。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不必费事了。每个人都会死的，你也不必太难过。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我死前，有两个愿望。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹说。",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "第一，你一定要利用这个机会除去唐傲，这是一个最好的时机，爹连死都不必装，一切都是真实的。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "第二，你一定要好好接管大风堂，完成我毕生的愿望。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_jian",
      "speaker_name": "赵简",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你一定要答应我。",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_zhao_jian",
      "text": "爹！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你人不错嘛！杀你父亲的仇人，你也掩埋，可见你对上官大叔，还是有蛮深厚的感情的，对不对？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我笑你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "笑我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，笑你很笨。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我很笨吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "当然，不笨，怎么会中了我的计呢",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "中你的计？什么计？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你知道你杀错好人了吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我杀错了谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "上官刃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "上官刃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "杀父仇人不该杀吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "该。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "那我怎么会杀错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "问题是，他不是你的杀父仇人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不相信？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我当然不相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "为什么不会？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么会？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为那是我编出来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你不觉得很可笑吗？我爹的日记是你编出来的？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我当然不信。你这样说有什么目的？你要故意逼我愤怒，是不是？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，我是故意要你感到懊悔，愤怒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这对你有什么好处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我可以趁机杀了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？我们不是有决斗之约在先吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "决斗？公平的决斗，我可没有把握胜得了你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为你跟萧东楼学的剑法，是天下第一的剑法，太厉害了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "所以你就故意要激怒我，让我冲动起来，对不对？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "但是，你编的故事未免太差了，我怎么可能相信你的话？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我有证据。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，这就是你爹的日记原本，我只不过利用一个临摹专家，学你爹的笔法来抄一遍而已。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你说的都是真的喽？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你亲眼目睹的证据，你还不相信？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "那你有什么感想？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我想杀你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你要替上官刃报仇？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "那我们上次的决斗之约，就取消喽？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们把日期改在今天？此时此地？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我不会反对。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我只后悔杀错了上官大叔。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "那这件事你是应该后悔的，其实，你这么容易受骗的人，实在是不应该出来领导大风堂的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你知道你应该做什么吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "赵无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "做鬼！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们现在就来进行公平的决斗吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    }
